This project aims to develop a mobile application to assist users in identifying mushrooms.
The app will utilize a machine learning model trained on a North American data set to
determine whether a mushroom is edible, based on its features. The app will also provide
educational resources to help users learn more about mushrooms. The goal is to create a
user-friendly and informative tool for mushroom foragers.
